The paper discusses troubleshooting machine learning systems, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The proposed methodology involves human computation tasks, which relates to human-computer interaction (cs.HCI). The paper also mentions measuring improvements in the holistic behavior of the system, which suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG). The example system used in the paper is an automated image captioning system, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). Finally, the paper discusses errors propagating and blame assignment, which suggests a focus on systems and control (cs.SY).
